## Final Note

This guide is current as of February 2026. The field is moving rapidly. Check Appendix A14 (Emerging Patterns & Community) quarterly for new developments. The core principles (context engineering, prompt-as-code, agent loops) will remain relevant, but tools and best practices will evolve.

Your greatest advantage as a CEO of an AI-native agency is that you can use these skills to multiply your own thinking and your team's leverage. Start with one skill, master it, then compose. That's how you'll build something remarkable.

Good luck.

